I"&<p>In order to render rst files in pycharm, you need to set up some environment
variables, otherwise youâ€™ll get the error <code>NameError: Cannot find docutils in selected interpreter.</code>
In short, you need to add</p>
<pre><code>export LC_ALL=en_US.UTF-8  
export LANG=en_US.UTF-8
</code></pre>
<p>to your <code>.bash_profile</code>. You can then restart pycharm and it should work.</p>

